    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s41746-025-01433-4 1.",
    "Adherence to Clinical Reasoning: KEEPER is constructed to emulate the diagnostic clinical reasoning process when applied to patient data by organizing structured data based on clinical presentation, disease history, preliminary diagnosis, diagnostic procedures, differential diagnoses, treatment, follow-up care, and complications. 2.",
    "Standardization: To ensure scalability and applicability across diverse data sources, data extraction is based on the OMOP CDM 10.",
    "KEEPER's outputs are standardized across diseases. 3.",
